title: Ep. #92 | Catching Up: Jamie Park
description:
Vocal powerhouse Jamie returns to DIVE Studios! Join Eric's former ASC co-host as she discusses her comeback single 'Apollo 11,' Mnet's reality series 'Good Girl,' and fans' reactions to her public name change. Also on the podcast, Jamie and Eric play a special segment of 'What Would Jamie Do?' Don't miss this hilarious reunion!
